{
  "id": "adv_card_ai_01_01",
  "title": "小美山愛 1話 いなくてもいい？",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0.03333333507180214
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――LizNoirが星見プロに移籍して",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――One day a while after LizNoir moved",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "しばらく経ったある日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "to Hoshimi Productions",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.459999962510734,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、お休みなのに\n時間をいただいてすみません……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ I'm sorry for taking time out of\nyour day off. ……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.966666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "いいよ、俺も休日の方が時間が取れるし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's okay‚ I'm free.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.066666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "そう言っていただけると助かります……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I appreciate you saying so…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.066666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "……ふぅ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…… Phew!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "今日は相談があるってことだけど……\nなんだか元気ないな。深刻なことなのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You said you have something to talk to me.\nYou're looking kind of down. Is it serious?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "い、いえ、{user}さんにとっては\nそんなに大したことじゃないんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "O-oh‚ no‚ it’s not\na big deal for {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.866666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "ただ、ちょっと私……\n芸能界引退しようかなって……あはは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's just that I'm a little ……\nI'm thinking of retiring …… haha ……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "大したことじゃないか！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's a very big deal!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.333333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "そんなによろけたら\n危ないですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's dangerous\nif you stagger so much!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんが怪我なんてしたら\n星見プロは大変です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If {user}-san gets injured‚\nHoshimi Pro will be in trouble.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "君が引退する方がもっと大変だよ！\nLizNoirのライブもようやく決まったのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's much harder for you to retire!\nLizNoir's live was finally scheduled…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.43333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "はい、ホントーに、すみません！　次のライブは\n莉央さん、葵さん、こころの三人体制で……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ really‚ I'm sorry!　The next live performance will be\nby Rio-san‚ Aoi-san and Kokoro…….",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "何があったんだ？　詳しく話してくれ\nもしかして、またこころに変なこと言われたとか――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What's going on?　Tell me the details.\nMaybe Kokoro said something strange to you again?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "い、いえ、こころは私にそんなこと絶対言いませんよ\nレッスンでアドバイスもしてくれますし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ no‚ Kokoro-chan would never say such a thing to me.\nShe’s always giving me advice during our lessons.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.33333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "一応言うけど、腹筋1000回ってこころに言われても\nしなくてもいいからな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just so you know‚ you don't have to do 1‚000 sit-ups‚\neven if Kokoro-chan tells you to.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-ai010.m4a",
      "text": "はい、それはもう冗談だって分かってます\n代わりに腕立て伏せが1000回になりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I already know that's a joke.\nInstead‚ I got 1‚000 pushups.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.63333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "それもウソというか、冗談だよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's also a lie……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.13333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "愛は素直過ぎだ……。辞めたいのはレッスンが\nキツ過ぎるとか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ai is too honest….\nSo you want to quit because the lessons are too hard or something?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-ai011.m4a",
      "text": "いえいえ！　レッスンが大変なのは当たり前です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ no‚ no!　It is normal for lessons to be difficult!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-ai012.m4a",
      "text": "私達、アイドルはファンのみなさんに最高のステージを\n観ていただくのが仕事ですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Our job as idols is to give our fans\nthe best stage performance possible.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "それが分かっているなら、愛は立派なアイドルだよ\nだったら、これからも――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you know that‚ then Ai is a fine idol.\nSo‚ then‚ I guess you can just keep――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-ai013.m4a",
      "text": "いいえ、私は立派なんかじゃありません……\nダメダメなんです……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ I'm not fine……\nI can do nothing…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.73333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-ai014.m4a",
      "text": "最近LizNoirの四人で通し稽古する機会があって\n改めて気付いたんです……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I recently had the opportunity to rehearse through the four of us in LizNoir‚\nand I noticed it again……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-ai015.m4a",
      "text": "私はLizNoirにはいらない子なんだって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "LizNoir doesn’t need me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "待ってくれ、そんなことはない。愛とこころが\n加入して、LizNoirはより人気が出たんだろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait‚ that's not true.\nLizNoir became more popular after Ai and Kokoro joined‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "海外での評価も高いじゃないか。愛はもう\nLizNoirには欠かせないメンバーに――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You've got a great reputation even abroad.\nAi is now an indispensable member of LizNoir――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-ai016.m4a",
      "text": "それは私じゃなくて、こころのお手柄です\nこころが強引に先輩方の考えを変えたからなんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's not me‚ that's Kokoro's work.\nIt's because Kokoro let the senpais to change their minds.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-ai017.m4a",
      "text": "こころはお調子者かもしれませんが、しっかりキャラを\n立てて、LizNoirの新しい魅力を引き出しました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kokoro may be a bit feisty‚ but she has a strong character‚\nbringing out a new charm for LizNoir!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.73333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-ai018.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんや葵さんのパフォーマンスのレベルの高さは\n言うまでもありません！　でも、私だけは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not to mention the high level of performance by Rio-san and Aoi-san!\nBut only me ……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-ai019.m4a",
      "text": "私だけは、添え物なんです\nいなくてもいい子なんですよーっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm the only garnish.\nI'm a girl who doesn't need to be there!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 174.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "（そうか、莉央さんや葵、それにこころと）\n（個性の強いメンバーで構成されている）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Well‚ with Rio‚ Aoi‚ and Kokoro…)\n(It consists of members with strong personalities.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 181.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "（愛だって充分魅力的な子なんだけど）\n（三人が強過ぎて、自信を失いかけてるんだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(But Ai is an attractive enough girl‚ too.)\n(The three of them are just so strong‚ so she lose confidence.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 188.16666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-ai020.m4a",
      "text": "そんなわけで、ライブが始まる前に\n引退の意向をお伝えしようと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's why I'm going to tell you about my intention to retire\nbefore the live starts…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 195.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "待ってくれ。愛がいらないなんて、誰も思ってない\n君はLizNoirには不可欠な存在だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait a minute. No one thinks Ai is a ganish.\nYou are an integral part of LizNoir.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 202.33333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-ai021.m4a",
      "text": "そうでしょうか……。このまま私が星見プロにいたら\nご迷惑がかかるんじゃ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm not sure if that's so. …… If I stay at Hoshimi Pro‚\nI'm afraid you're going to have trouble because of me……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 209.66666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-ai022.m4a",
      "text": "私のことだったら気にしないで下さい\n実家のラーメン屋を継ぎますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't worry if it's about me.\nI'm taking over my family's ramen shop.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 214.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-ai023.m4a",
      "text": "これでも結構、麺上げはうまいって\n父も褒めてくれて――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm pretty good at simming noddles‚ tho.\nMy father was very complimentary of my work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 220.26666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "愛、LizNoirには君が必要だ。それに君には\n間違いなくアイドルの才能がある",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ai‚ LizNoir needs you.\nAnd you definitely have the talent of an idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 226.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "でも、不安を抱えたまま続けるのも酷だとは思う\nだから俺にマネージャーの仕事をさせてほしい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I don't think it's too much to ask to continue with the uncertainty.\nSo let me do the manager thing to support.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 234.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-ai024.m4a",
      "text": "マネージャーのお仕事ですか？\nでも、いつもちゃんとお仕事してますよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Manager thing?\nBut you always do your job well‚ don't you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 239.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルの魅力を引き出すのが、俺の一番大切な仕事だ\nライブまでに、君の魅力をもっと引き出して見せる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My most important job is to bring out the best in my idols.\nI'll bring out more of your charm before the live.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 248.16666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-ai025.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……\nそこまで私を……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san……\nYou are doing all these for me……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 253.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-ai026.m4a",
      "text": "……は、はい！　分かりました！\nふつつか者ですが、よろしくお願いいたします！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "……Alright!　Understood!\nI know I'm not good enough‚ but thank you in advance for your help!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 259.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-koh018.m4a",
      "text": "なんだか、嫁入りみたいな挨拶だな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's kind of like a marriage greeting tho.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 264.1666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-ai027.m4a",
      "text": "あわわ！　嫁入りだなんて、そんな……！\nすみませんすみません！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aww!　I can't believe you're a bride-to-be. ……\nSorry‚ sorry!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 270.6333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-koh019.m4a",
      "text": "い、いや……俺のほうこそ悪かったよ……\n謝らないでくれ。そんな所も愛の魅力なんだから",
      "translations": {
